; Minimal qfasm2 range proof extension.
;
; This crosses qfasm2's common N220 code-size boundary by one byte without
; loading a broad range table.

(Add N0 N221) N221
(FileSize N221) (Bytes 31 01 00 00)
(FileSize N233) (Bytes 3D 01 00 00)
(Addr N221) (Bytes 31 81 04 08)

(Inc N221) N222
(Inc N222) N223
(Inc N223) N224
(Inc N224) N225
(Inc N225) N226
(Inc N226) N227
(Inc N227) N228
(Inc N228) N229
(Inc N229) N230
(Inc N230) N231
(Inc N231) N232
(Inc N232) N233

(Size (BigExit42N221)) N221

(Rule
  (Pass2 (Ins (BigExit42N221) rest) pc sym)
  (Bytes 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 90 B8 01 00 00 00 BB 2A 00 00 00 CD 80 (Pass2 rest (Add pc N221) sym)))
